Build project:
Compiled in OSX 10.11.4, Macbook Pro.

cd [project directory]
cd build
make
./ simulation [1, 2, 3]

[1, 2, 3] is the command line argument for switching scene.

Scene 1:
Curtain simulation, with collision detection with the ball.
[W, A, S, D] Move the ball, in x-z plane.
[J, K, I, L] Rotate the camera.
[-, =] Zoom in/out.

Scene 2:
Running cubeman with a cape.
[left arrow, right arrow] rotate camera in x axis.

Scene 3:
For fun.